{
  "stem": "13911.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and my, this is how my mind only speeds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If I survive, I'll-- I'll eat so much cake and jam.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And they said, yeah, if you survive and you get married-- At that time, it was customary to give the [NON-ENGLISH], dowry.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We'll give you a big, if you survive, a big jar of jam they're gonna give me for my wedding.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I say, I'll jump into the jar, and I'll-- I'll dwell in it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I-- I-- I really don't know what?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We ate very little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever somebody could sneak in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was there enough water to drink?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Water, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Water, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, water, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just remember my most favorite-- favorite-- The meal that I can't forget the taste, and I'm still searching for it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were two boys, and they were taken to an oil refinery that was like in the outskirts of our town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they sneaked out of that oil refinery, a little bottle of oil, and they gave us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somewhere we found a tomato.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And not tomatoes were good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not much, like I eat it because you have to, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not much, but our tomatoes-- Because it wasn't like here, that they are artificially ripened, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were straight from the garden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- and the girls got up that tomato, some salt, and that oil that they brought, a little-- I think that this was the most heavenly taste.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm still, when I'm looking at tomatoes, I'm searching for a tomato that maybe would taste like the one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the best tomato that you ever had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was so heavenly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was not like a-- this kind of a eater.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, I'd rather, I would talk about heavenly food, I'll talk about cake.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
